; IE-EnableScriptErrors.reg
; Enable "Display a notification about every script error" in Internet Explorer
;
; Blog Post: https://sharepointyankee.com/internet-explorer-registry-shortcuts-for-enabling-and-disabling-scripting-error-notifications
; Author: Geoff Varosky
; Website: https://sharepointyankee.com

Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Main]
"Error Dlg Displayed On Every Error"="yes"
